						               													<description>Which is the best herding dog in the valley of the hungry wolves? Shouting &amp;ldquo;Woof!&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Baa&amp;rdquo; the players move round the meadow. It&amp;rsquo;s now or never to catch up with the next dog and be the first to collect three sheep and win this romping die game for 2-4 players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hungry Wolves (W&amp;uuml;rfelw&amp;ouml;lfe) is a hectic action game with dice. The players circle a flock of sheep with their herding dogs. All players throw their dice simultaneously and have to perform an action as fast as possible depending on the dice throw, e.g. saying &amp;quot;Woof!&amp;quot; or running around the table. &amp;#10;Also, the movement of the dog depends on the dice throw.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As soon as the action is performed, the dice throwing continues. When one dog reaches or overtakes another, the round ends and the faster dog gets a sheep from the flock as a reward.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is on the recommendation list of the SdJ-jury 2009.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
